response.overview: You always have that suspicion that something funny goes on in those frat houses when no one is around. I mean, all those guys living together, drinking together, and together... are you telling me that they never fool around with each other? Top Dog took the age old question into some of the local frat houses and what they found will blow your mind... or turn you on! There's a whole lot of jerkin', suckin', and fuckin' going on in this frat house!
response.title: Frat Boys: Behind Closed Doors
